---
/**
 * rest-api/0003 · Figure 2 — "method semantics · RFC 9110": GET/PUT/DELETE are
 * idempotent, POST is not.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the source HTML (figure + svg + figcaption). Lives as an
 * .astro component (not inline MDX) for the same kebab-case-SVG reason as Fig1.
 * This figure references no arrow markers, so no local <defs> is needed.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 560 120" role="img" aria-label="GET, PUT, DELETE are idempotent; POST is not">
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif" font-size="11">
            <text
                x="280"
                y="16"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">METHOD SEMANTICS · RFC 9110</text
            >
            <rect x="8" y="30" width="128" height="60" rx="9" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect>
            <text x="72" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="700" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >GET</text
            >
            <text x="72" y="74" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >✓ idempotent · safe</text
            >
            <rect x="144" y="30" width="128" height="60" rx="9" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="208"
                y="56"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="14"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">PUT</text
            >
            <text x="208" y="74" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >✓ replaces → converges</text
            >
            <rect x="280" y="30" width="128" height="60" rx="9" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="344"
                y="56"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="14"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">DELETE</text
            >
            <text x="344" y="74" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >✓ idempotent</text
            >
            <rect x="416" y="30" width="136" height="60" rx="9" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="484"
                y="56"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="14"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#9a2417">POST</text
            >
            <text x="484" y="74" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >✗ creates each time</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        <code>PUT /orders/42</code> replaces a known resource — two calls converge. <code
            >POST /orders</code
        > mints a new one each time.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
